<item>
            <title>[SOLR-8626] [ANGULAR] 404 error when clicking nodes in cloud graph view</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8626</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;Reproduce%3A&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Reproduce:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;bin/solr start -c&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;bin/solr create -c mycoll&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Goto &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8983/solr/#/~cloud&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8983/solr/#/~cloud&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Click a collection name in the graph -&amp;gt; 404 error. URL: &lt;tt&gt;/solr/mycoll/#/~cloud&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Click a shard name in the graph -&amp;gt; 404 error. URL: &lt;tt&gt;/solr/shard1/#/~cloud&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Only verified in Trunk, but probably exists in 5.4 as well&lt;/p&gt;</description>
